content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 410.1 - Application of rules of the workers' compensation board to the volunteer ambulance workers' benefit law

State Regulations

All rules of the board under the Workers' Compensation Law
are hereby made applicable to proceedings under the Volunteer Ambulance

Workers' Benefit Law to the extent that such rules are not inconsistent with
the Volunteer Ambulance Workers' Benefit Law or any future rule adopted by the
board thereunder. Notes
